~~لعلكم تفلحون }
# Allah, the, Exalted says:
# "And all of you beg Allah to forgive you, O believers, that you may be
~~successful". (24:31)
# وقال تعالى ( هود 3 ) : { استغفروا ربكم ثم توبوا إليه }
# "Seek the forgiveness of your Rubb, and turn to Him in repentance". (11:3)
