~~of Allah (PBUH) said, "The strong man is not one who is good at
~~wrestling, but the strong man is one who controls himself in a fit of
~~rage.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith instructs oneself to keep in control in order
