~~من الموبقات ] رواه البخاري
# وقال [ الموبقات ] : المهلكات.
# . 63- Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) said: You indulge in (bad)
~~actions which are more insignificant to you than a hair while we
~~considered them at the time of Messenger of Allah (PBUH) to be great
~~destroying sins".
# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: The less fear of Allah, one has the more disobedient he
~~becomes to Him. As the fear of Allah decreases, one becomes more bold in
~~committing sins. As the Companions of the Prophet (PBUH) were intensely
~~fearful of Allah, they were afraid of committing even very minor sins.
