~~clothing of Me and I shall clothe you. O My slaves, you commit sins
~~night and day and I forgive all sins, so seek My forgiveness and I shall
~~forgive you. O My slaves, you can neither do Me any harm nor can you do
~~Me any good. O My slaves, were the first of you and the last of you, the
