~~good works he used to do when he was healthy or at home".
# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: This Hadith refers to the actions which a Muslim should
~~take to gain the Blessings of Allah and acceptance of his prayers by
~~Him, because one is duty-bound to fulfil all his obligations in all
~~circumstances.
