~~Allah and His Prophet (PBUH) without `ifs' and `buts.' Hairsplitting in
~~religious issues falls in this category. It opens the door for chaos and
~~conflict and paves the way for disunity and separation. May Allah give
~~sense to the Muslim Ummah to abandon this road and take the Right Path
~~which ensures peace and security. Let it be absolutely clear that the
~~Right Path is one and one alone. There cannot be multiple right paths,
~~it is one and singular. Once a community leaves the Straight Path, it is
~~sure to go astray.
