~~the poor of that place. If some amount is left unspent only then it
~~should be distributed among the deserving people of other areas.
# 3. The collectors of Zakat should refrain from aggression in its
~~collection as in that case they will be invoking the curse of the people
~~concerned and thereby invite the Wrath of Allah
