# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: It will be indeed a great honour to be close to the
~~Prophet (PBUH) in Jannah. This honour will be given to those who are
~~kind to the orphans. The Prophet (PBUH) has regarded it the `best house'
~~in which an orphan is treated with kindness. He declared the worst home
~~in which an orphan child is not treated with affection.
