~~of Allah (PBUH) said, "He who believes in Allah and the Last Day let him
~~not harm his neighbour; and he who believes in Allah and the Last Day
~~let him show hospitality to his guest; and he who believes in Allah and
~~the Last Day let him speak good or remain silent".
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith unfolds the fruits of Faith. One who does not
~~have the qualities mentioned in it, is deprived of the blessings of the
~~Faith. Faith of such a person is like a fruitless tree, or a flower
~~without fragrance, or a body without soul.
