# 363. Abu Musa Al-Ash`ari (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: I
~~heard the Prophet (PBUH) saying, "The similitude of good company and
~~that of bad company is that of the owner of musk and of the one blowing
~~the bellows. The owner of musk would either offer you some free of
