~~Prophet (PBUH) said, "Seven are (the persons) whom Allah will give Shade
~~of His Thrown on the Day when there would be no shade other than His
~~Throne's Shade: A just ruler; a youth who grew up worshipping Allah; a
~~man whose heart is attached to mosques; two persons who love and meet
~~each other and depart from each other for the sake of Allah; a man whom
~~an extremely beautiful woman seduces (for illicit relation), but he
~~(rejects this offer by saying): `I fear Allah'; a man who gives in
