~~above those which have been mentioned here. Some `Ulama' including As-
~~Sakhkhawi and Al-Hafiz Ibn Hajar have given a list of seventy such
~~actions. Imam As-Suyuti said: "The (present) Hadith mentions only seven
~~qualities to bring into prominence their importance and also the
~~importance of acting upon them'.
