~~seventy thousand angels, pulling it".
# [Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith deals with the hidden matters relating to the
~~Unseen world. Muslims are ordained by Allah to believe in them. It is
~~wrong to hold them as metaphorical. They are realities but we can not
~~imagine them.
