# . Mu`adh bin Jabal (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: I was
~~riding a pillion with the Prophet (PBUH) on a donkey. He (PBUH) said, "O
~~Mu`adh, do you know what is the right of Allah upon His slaves, and what
