~~(PBUH) to seek punishment for his wrongdoing is said to have been Abul-
~~Yusr Ka`b bin `Amr whose story was also mentioned in the previous
~~Hadith. The sin he had committed was not a major one that is why by
~~Salat it was wiped out.
