# Allah, the Exalted, says:
# "Verily, the likeness of (this) worldly life is as the water (rain)
~~which We send down from the sky; so by it arises the intermingled
~~produce of the earth of which men and cattle eat: until when the earth
~~is clad in its adornments and is beautified, and its people think that
~~they have all the powers of disposal over it, Our Command reaches it by
~~night or by day and We make it like a clean-mown harvest, as if it had
~~not flourished yesterday! Thus, do We explain the Ayat (proofs,
~~evidences, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, laws, etc.) in detail
~~for the people who reflect.'' (10:24)
