~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "Begging is a cut that a person inflicts
~~upon his face; except for asking a ruler, or under the stress of
~~circumstances from which there is no escape.''
# [At-Tirmidhi].
# Commentary: To submit his demand to the Head of state means that if a
~~man deserves help, he should go to the public treasury which exists in
~~an Islamic country so as to fulfill the needs of the needy gracefully.
~~If his access to it is not possible, he is free to put his demand to
~~others as well.
