~~except its shoulder.''
# [At-Tirmidhi].
# Commentary: This Hadith reveals a truth to man that he should not eat
~~up anything and everything all alone, rather in this regard he is
~~supposed to take the maximum care for the distribution of alms and
~~charity so that it may stand him in good stead in the Hereafter. What
~~one has given in charity will by no means be wasted, for he will
~~doubtlessly find its reward with Allah on the Day of Resurrection.
