# 582. `Aishah (May Allah be pleased with her): reported Whenever it was
~~her turn to spend with Messenger of Allah (PBUH), he used to go to the
~~Baqi` (graveyard in Al-Madinah) at the last part of night and say, "May
~~you be safe, O abode of the believing people. What you have been
~~promised has come to you. You are tarried till tomorrow and certainly we
