~~to despise anybody on the basis of wealth, social distinction and
~~lineage. Moreover, one should also not adopt an unkind attitude towards
~~others. Besides, if Allah has bestowed honour on somebody, he is
~~supposed to be grateful to Him, instead of behaving disrespectfully
~~towards people and subjecting them to unkindness and tyranny.
