~~everywhere but the decision to send a man either to Jannah or to Hell
~~will not be taken capriciously. Rather set Divine rules will be working
~~behind it. Allah, will place some people in Jannah due to their good
~~deeds; similarly he will place some people in Hell due to their bad
~~deeds. Allah does not wrong anyone.
