~~on account of their wild temperament and foolishness. A kind handling is
~~indispensable for putting them to discipline, even if they make
~~desperate blunders. This Hadith is very beneficial with regard to the
~~way of Da`wah, guidance and practical education. Another point this
~~Hadith discloses is that the flow of water can wipe out dirt and
~~impurity, and make the place free from its effect.
