~~that owing to their lack of talent they will mismanage the task which
~~will be assigned to them. This will render them guilty with Allah. The
~~Prophet (PBUH) dissuades such people from accepting any government
~~portfolio as in this way they will remain safe and trouble-free. Yet, if
~~a deserving person gets a job of high responsibility, he should do his
~~utmost to do full justice to it, so that he may be spared remorse on the
~~Day of Resurrection.
