# Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith speaks about the simplicity and humility of
~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) with regard to food. As he abstained from a
~~luxurious lifestyle, he hardly craved for delicious food. No mention of
~~dainties, he would readily eat whatever was available to him.
