# 747. Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: I saw Messenger of
~~Allah (PBUH) eating some dates while sitting on his buttocks, with his
~~legs raised.
# [Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith sheds light on another sitting posture of
~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH). But it betrays his uneasy state. In fact,
~~when he was in a hurry he would be eager by eating a few dates so that
~~he might be free to attend to some more important business. Also a
~~report of Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) quoted by Muslim explains
~~this state of mind of Messenger of Allah (PBUH).
