~~left over from last night, give it to us for drinking; otherwise, we
~~shall drink from some stream directly.''
# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: With reference to this Hadith, Imam An-Nawawi says that
~~apart from drinking water from a vessel, one can also drink at a cistern
~~or stream.
