# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: There are many kinds of silk. But the real silk is that
~~which is naturally spun by the silkworm. However, the artificially
~~manufactured silk is also available nowadays. Men are not under ban to
~~use it. But there are certain varieties of such cloth which are used
~~only by women. These are forbidden to men. Besides, they are disallowed
~~to sit on a silk cloth. Similarly, quilts, mattresses and pillows should
~~not be made from it because both men and women use them.
