~~always perform thirteen Rak`ah in the Tahajjud prayer. This Hadith
~~further tells us that after his midnight prayer, the Prophet (PBUH)
~~would perform two Rak`ah of Sunnah (i.e., after the Adhan of Fajr
~~prayer) and then lie down on his right side. This practice of Messenger
~~of Allah (PBUH) is an established fact.
