# 835. Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Messenger
~~of Allah (PBUH) said, "Those people who leave a gathering in which they
~~have not remembered Allah, will conclude it as if it has foul odour
~~similar to that of a rotten carcass of a donkey. And it will be a cause
~~of grief to them.''
# [Abu Dawud].
# Commentary: Messenger of Allah (PBUH) has warned us against refraining
~~from the remembrance of Allah because most of the heart diseases are
~~caused by this indifference, and because most of the sins are committed
~~as a result of this indifference.
