# Allah, the Exalted, says:
# "O you who believe! Enter not houses other than your own, until you
~~have asked permission and greeted those in them.'' (24:27)
# "But when you enter the houses, greet one another with a greeting from
~~Allah (i.e., say: As-Salamu `alaikum - peace be on you), blessed and
~~good.'' (24:61)
