~~الكثير ] متفق عليه
# وفي رواية للبخاري : والصغير على الكبير
# 857. Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Messenger
~~of Allah (PBUH) said, 'A rider should greet a pedestrian; a pedestrian
~~should greet one who is sitting; and a small group should greet a large
~~group (of people).''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# The narration in Al-Bukhari adds: Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "The
~~young should greet the elderly.''
# Commentary: The greeting of As-Salamu Alaikum should be uttered
~~according to the prescribed way. It is the situations under reference
~~and not the grades which will be taken into consideration in this
~~respect.
