# 862. Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) reported that he passed by
~~some children and greeted them. Then he said: "Messenger of Allah (PBUH)
~~used to do the same.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: By greeting children, we please their hearts and also vent
~~our modesty. Besides, the importance of As-Salam is unconsciously felt
~~by them. Above all it is the Sunnah of the Messenger of Allah (PBUH) and
~~so we are supposed to put it into practice.
