~~will be a) purification (from sins), if Allah wills].''
# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: According to this Hadith, a patient should be told that
~~his disease will purge out his sins. To sit beside the sick, to comfort
~~his heart and to say a few words of sympathy to him was the Prophet's
~~practice.
