~~prayed to Allah for its alleviation and sought His Help. Sheikh Al-
~~Albani considers the authenticity of this Hadith as deficient. However,
~~the Prophet (PBUH) is authentically reported to have lost consciousness
~~during severe illness. Both the Ahadith of this chapter reveal that man
~~should seek help from Allah at the hour of his departure from this world.
