~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) encamped at night during a journey, he would
~~lie down on his right side, and when he stayed a little before dawn he
~~would raise his forearm and place his head on the palm of his hand.
# [Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith tells us that we should be fully regardful of
~~the performance of prayer, particularly during a journey. We must make
~~sure we perform prayer at the right time.
