# 964. Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: The Messenger of
~~Allah (PBUH) said, "Keep to travelling by night because the earth is
~~folded (traversed more easily) during the night.''
# [Abu Dawud].
# Commentary: According to this Hadith, we should preferably travel at
~~night, particularly late at night. After having slept in the first part
~~of night, one feels invigorated and fresh enough to restart one's
~~journey.
