# The word "Ghina'' is ordinarily used for singing but here it means the
~~recitation which is done in accordance with the principles of Tajwid and
~~in a beautiful voice.
# Thus, this Hadith induces us to recite the Qur'an properly with nice
~~feeling and voice.
