~~المساجد وانتظار الصلاة بعد الصلاة فذلكم الرباط فذلكم الرباط ] رواه مسلم
# 1030. Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported that the
~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "Shall I not tell you something by which
~~Allah effaces the sins and elevates ranks (in Jannah)?'' The Companions
~~said; "Certainly, O Messenger of Allah.'' He (PBUH) said, "Performing
~~the Wudu' thoroughly in spite of difficult circumstances, walking with
~~more paces to the mosque, and waiting for the next As-Salat (the prayer)
