# [Muslim].
# Commentary: Hardship and unpleasantness here stand for the uneasiness
~~that one feels while performing Wudu' in severe cold. Ar-Ribat means
~~watching the frontiers or battlefront to check the invasion of the
~~enemy. To wait for the next Salat after offering a Salat is regarded as
~~Ribat for the reason that by so doing, a person who is particular in
~~offering Salat keeps himself constantly engaged in the obedience and
~~worship of Allah to keep Satan away from him.
