~~that there so no true god except Allah Alone, Who has no partners and
~~that Muhammad ((PBUH) is His slave and Messenger],' the eight gates of
~~Jannah are opened for him. He may enter through whichever of these gates
~~he desires (to enter).''
# [Muslim].
