~~tawwabina, waj-`alni minal-mutatahhirin (O Allah make me among those who
~~repent and purify themselves).''
# Commentary: Tahur (means Wudu' which is the foremost condition for
~~Salat. One is not permitted to perform Salat without Wudu' in the
