~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) saying, "If three men in a village or in the
~~desert, make no arrangement for Salat in congregation, Satan must have
~~certainly overcome them. So observe Salat in congregation, for the wolf
~~eats up a solitary sheep that stays far from the flock.''
# [Abu Dawud].
# Commentary: This Hadith also stresses the importance of offering Salat
~~in congregation and mentions the disadvantages of offering it
~~individually. One who remains aloof from the congregation, is like the
~~sheep which is separated from its herd and becomes a victim of the wolf.
~~One who lives alone is easily overpowered by satanic doubts.
