~~(PBUH) is His slave and Messenger; performing of Salat (Iqamat-as-
~~Salat); the payment of Zakat; performing Hajj (pilgrimage) to the House
~~[of Allah (Ka`bah)]; and Saum (fasting) during the month of Ramadan.''
