# Commentary: In this Hadith, Islam has been compared to a building
~~which rests on five pillars. As a building cannot stand without its
~~foundation, similarly, Islam cannot exist without these pillars. For
~~this reason, he who denies any one of these obligations is a
~~disbeliever, and he who neglects any of them due to slackness or want of
~~attention is a sinful and impious Muslim.
