~~technically. In the former case, it is a miracle of the Prophet (PBUH)
~~while in the latter it is Wahy (Revelation). Almighty Allah informed him
~~that Satan enters the rows of the people offering prayers through the
~~spaces left by them in their rows. Satan is pleased to see these gaps as
~~they make his task of creating doubts in the minds of worshippers easy.
