~~homes).''
# [Muslim]
# Commentary: This Hadith has the same message which is conveyed by the
~~preceding Ahadith namely that the Fard Salat should be performed in the
~~Masjid (mosque) while some of the supererogatory, optional and voluntary
~~prayers should be performed at home.
