~~the night is attended (by the angels), and that is better.''
# [Muslim].
# Commentary: If a person is confident that he will get up to perform
~~Witr prayer before dawn, it is better for him to perform it in the late
~~hours of the night; otherwise, it will be well to do so after `Isha'
