~~become utterly unmindful of the remembrance of Allah and His Orders.
~~Such people are Munafiqun (hypocrites), whose abode will be Hell. It
~~means that negligence of Jumu`ah for a long time is such a serious
~~offence that it can even seal a man's heart, which finishes all hopes
~~and chances of one's improvement.
