~~ويصوم يوما ويفطر يوما ] متفق عليه
# 1177. `Abdullah bin `Amr (May Allah be pleased with them) reported:
~~The Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "The Salat which is dearest to Allah
~~is that of (Prophet) Dawud; and As-Saum (the fasting) which is dearest
~~to Allah is that of (Prophet) Dawud. He used to sleep half the night,
