~~(PBUH) said, "Trim the moustaches and let the beard grow.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: Ahfu means trim excessively. Thus, keeping of long
~~moustaches will be against this injunction. The meanings of the word
~~A`fu have been stated above, that is, leave the beard to follow its
~~natural growth.
