~~Every Muslim who has fifty-two and a half Tola (a Tola is about 12
~~grams) silver or cash equivalent to it in excess of his need, and a year
~~has passed since its possession is liable to pay it. One who has seven
~~and a half Tola or more gold also comes in this category. It should be
~~evaluated in terms of money and Zakat at the rate of 2.5% to be paid on it.
