~~قدر خمسون آية . متفق عليه
# 1230. Zaid bin Thabit (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: We
~~took Suhur (predawn meal) with the Messenger of Allah (PBUH) and then we
~~stood up for (Fajr) Salat (prayer). It was asked: "How long was the gap
~~between the two?'' He replied: "The time required for the recitation of
