# 1271. Ibn `Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) reported: The
~~Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "(The superstructure of) Islam is based
~~on five (pillars), testifying the fact that La ilaha illallah wa anna
~~Muhammad-ar-Rasul-ullah [there is no true god except Allah, and Muhammad
~~((PBUH)) is the Messenger of Allah], establishing As-Salat (the
