~~(Ka`bah)], and the Saum (fasting) during the month of Ramadan.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: This Hadith has been mentioned earlier. Here it has been
~~repeated in support of the obligation of the fourth pillar of Islam.
~~Thus, Hajj is compulsory for a person who fulfills the qualifications
~~required for it and has the means for it.
