# 1319. Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Umm Ar-Rubaiy`i
~~bint Al-Bara', who was the mother of Harithah bin Suraqah, came to the
~~Prophet (PBUH) and said: "O Messenger of Allah! Will you not tell me
~~about Harithah? (He was killed in the battle of Badr). If he is in
