~~to give more than the agreed (quality/weight/number of goods etc.)
~~against the settled price. This is a step ahead of justice - that is
~~Ihsan, which has very salutary effects on society. On the contrary, if
~~people are in the habit of encroaching up others' rights, it will
~~doubtless create jealousy and enmity, which are ruinous to the society.
