~~You Who have majesty and nobility)!'' (Imam) Al-Awza`i, one of the
~~narrators of this Hadith, was asked: "How forgiveness is to be sought?''
~~He answered: "The Messenger of Allah (PBUH) used to say:
~~`Astaghfirullah! Astaghfirullah! (I beseech Allah for forgiveness, I
~~beseech Allah for forgiveness)'.''
