~~that man with a squint who will appear before the Day of Judgement. This
~~is why he is called Al-Masih Ad-Dajjal. He will make claim of godhood
~~and in order to test the Faith of people, Allah will get some
~~supernatural works done from him. The pious ones would, however,
~~recognize him and will save themselves from his trap. This will be a
~~great trial indeed and one must seek refuge with Allah from it.
