~~The Messenger of Allah (PBUH) and I went to see a woman. She had date-
~~stones or pebbles in front of her, and she was counting and reciting
~~Tasbih. [`Subhan-Allah' (Allah is free from imperfection)]. He said,
~~"Shall I not inform you of what is easier or better than this for you?''
~~You should say: `Subhan-Allahi `adada ma khalaqa fis-sama', wa subhan-
