# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: The prayer mentioned in this Hadith is, in fact, a
~~Muslim's declaration to turn in every matter to Allah, and to care about
~~His Pleasure and His Orders regarding every act. It is also a
~~declaration to befriend people for His sake and to show enmity towards
~~people for Him alone. May Allah give every Muslim the ability to make
~~this prayer and to act according to the declaration that he makes
