### ||| AUTO 1564 - وعن عائشة رضي الله عنها قالت قال رسول الله صلى الله
~~عليه وسلم : [ لا تسبوا الأموات فإنهم قد أفضوا إلى ما قدموا ] رواه
~~البخاري
# 1564. `Aishah (May Allah be pleased with her) said: The Messenger of
~~Allah (PBUH) said, "Do not abuse the dead, because they have attained
~~that which they had forwarded (i.e., their deeds, good or bad).''
# [Al-Bukhari].
# Commentary: We learn from this Hadith that we should not censure or
~~condemn the deceased because they have reached their end and they are
~~receiving in the Hereafter return for whatever deeds they did in their
~~life. There is no harm, however, in abusing the disbelievers who died in
~~a state of Kufr.
PageV01P1995
