# 1569. Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) said: The Prophet
~~(PBUH) said, "Beware of envy because envy consumes (destroys) the
~~virtues just as the fire consumes the firewood,'' or he said "grass.''
# [Abu Dawud].
# Commentary: Envy is one of the major sins which are bound to destroy
~~virtues as fast as the fire burns the wood and dry grass to ashes.
