# 1. This Hadith has a stern warning for those who punish their slaves
~~and servants without reason or far more than what they deserve.
# 2. This Hadith also gives a hint of the aura of awe and majesty that
~~characterized the person of the Prophet (PBUH). It also shows the
~~readiness of the Companions to mend their ways and obey the Prophet's
~~commands.
PageV01P2066
