~~there to talk.'' Thereupon the Messenger of Allah (PBUH) said, "If you
~~have to sit at all, then fulfill the rights of the road.'' They asked:
~~"What are their rights?'' Thereupon he said, "Lowering the gaze (so that
~~you may not stare at unlawful things); refraining from doing some harm
~~to others, responding to greeting (i.e., saying `Wa`alaikumus-salam' to
~~one another) and commanding the good and forbidding the evil.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: Since roads, streets, lanes and all thoroughfares are the
