# [Abu Dawud with a good Isnad].
# Commentary: We learn from this Hadith that it is undesirable to put on
~~one's shoes (or socks, etc.) in the standing position. Some religious
~~scholars are of the opinion that this is more of an advice than an
~~order. By prescribing the manners of wearing one's shoes, it has been
~~illustrated that the Islamic teachings cover all spheres of life.
