# 1663. Ibn `Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) said: The Messenger
~~of Allah (PBUH) visited Sa`d bin `Ubadah during his illness. He was
~~accompanied by `Abdur-Rahman bin `Auf, Sa`d bin Abu Waqqas and `Abdullah
