~~future is such a great offense that he who does it, loses all merits of
~~his forty days Salat. Some people try to detect the culprits involved in
~~a theft case through the so-called fortunetellers or seek their advice
~~in matters relating to business, marriage etc. All such things are
~~unlawful because Allah Alone knows the invisible world.
