# 1739. `Aishah (May Allah be pleased with her) said: The Prophet (PBUH)
~~said, "None of you should say: `My soul has become evil.' He should say:
~~`My soul is in bad shape.'''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: Khabusatu and Laqisatu are synonymous but the former has
~~appearance of greater sinfulness. Imam Al-Khattabi says that this is a
~~guidance for speaking in a proper manner. One should always use a decent
~~word and abstain from impolite language.
