~~Allah (PBUH) said, "When one of you supplicates, let him be decisive and
~~he should not say: `O Allah, bestow upon me such and such if You wish',
~~because no one has the power to compel Him.''
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: One should pray to Allah will full confidence that He will
~~answer his prayers. One should also persist in praying and never give in
~~to despair.
