# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# 1765. Ibn `Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) said: The Messenger
~~of Allah (PBUH) prohibited observing continuous fasts beyond one day.
~~The Companions submitted: "But you do it.'' He replied, "I am not like
