~~wife.''
# "Leaving the animals unmilked'' means that a saleable cattle is not
~~milked for two or three times to create an impression that the cattle is
~~rich in milk, which is not the true case. This is also prohibited. Other
~~points mentioned in this Hadith have been discussed earlier.
