~~acquisition of property wrongfully.
# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: The matters mentioned in this Hadith have been discussed
~~in detail before. What this Hadith specially brings out is that the
~~custom or writing or dictating Ahadith existed even during the age of
~~the Companions. In this respect that was the first period of the
~~compilation of Ahadith. Thus, it is wrong to say that there did not
~~exist any system of recording Hadith in the days of the Companions.
