~~said: Indeed, this man has disobeyed Abul-Qasim (PBUH).
# [Muslim].
# Commentary: We learn from this Hadith that after hearing Adhan, one
~~should not leave the mosque without offering the obligatory Salat
~~connected with it, unless one has a very genuine reason for doing so.
