# [Al-Bukhari and Muslim].
# Commentary: Dibaj is a kind of silk. Some say that thick silk is
~~called Dibaj. Others say that it is the type of cloth in which some of
~~the lengthwise and breadthwise threads are of pure silk, while the rest
~~of the cloth is made of cotton.
