~~his talk. Some of those present thought that he had heard him but
~~disliked the interruption and the other said that he had not hear him.
~~When the Messenger of Allah (PBUH) concluded his speech he asked, "Where
~~is the one who inquired about the Last Day?'' The man replied: "Here I
~~am.'' The Messenger of Allah (PBUH) replied, "When the practice of
~~honouring a trust is lost, expect the Last Day.'' He asked: "How could
