~~Judgement has been mentioned: The affairs of the world will be in the
~~hands of wicked and undeserving people. The sinners and wicked people
~~will become the leaders of the world. The preaching pulpits would also
~~be occupied by people who would be greedy and ignorant.They will be
~~devoid of piety and abstinence.
