~~(15:45-48)
# "(It will be said to the believers of Islamic Monotheism): `My slaves!
~~No fear shall be on you this Day, nor shall you grieve. (You) who
~~believed in Our Ayat (proofs, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.)
